      • getColumn

        public java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> getColumn(java.lang.String column,
                                                       java.lang.String artist,
                                                       java.lang.String album,
                                                       java.lang.String title)
        Method that obtains only a single tag column from the songs in the database. In addition to filtering parameters of the method, the content of the 'filter' table is taken into account, which filters songs according to the set of chords that they contain (obviously only matters for the Chord type of a song)
        Parameters:
        artist - Regex string that should match the songs artist field
        album - Regex string that should match the songs album field
        title - Regex string that should match the songs title field
        column - Column to be extracted from the song tags
        Returns:
        An ArrayList of strings containing the requested tag column

      • setFilter

        Sets the content of the 'filter' table
        Parameters:
        chordFilter - An Array containing the chord_ids as found in the 'chords' table
